          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9789898657725" href="/book/show/22913619-o-signo-dos-quatro">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=e-4">e-4</a>, 
