<span id="freeTextContainer7058784045717522305">Even though I watched every series and movie about Sherlock Holmes, I&apos;ve read only <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8921.The_Hound_of_the_Baskervilles__Sherlock_Holmes___5_' title='The Hound of the Baskervilles (Sherlock Holmes, #5) by Arthur Conan Doyle' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Hound of the Baskervilles</a> 30 years ago. And I have to admit that I should&apos;ve read it earlier for it is truly the master piece!<br/>I love Sherlock! His twisted mind, his vices, his madness. And the ingenuity in solving mysteries. Audiobook was fantastic, narrator is excellent. And I will surely look for other Sherlock adventures.</span>
  <span id="freeText7058784045717522305" style="display:none">Even though I watched every series and movie about Sherlock Holmes, I've read only <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8921.The_Hound_of_the_Baskervilles__Sherlock_Holmes___5_" title="The Hound of the Baskervilles (Sherlock Holmes, #5) by Arthur Conan Doyle" rel="nofollow noopener">The Hound of the Baskervilles</a> 30 years ago. And I have to admit that I should've read it earlier for it is truly the master piece!<br />I love Sherlock! His twisted mind, his vices, his madness. And the ingenuity in solving mysteries. Audiobook was fantastic, narrator is excellent. And I will surely look for other Sherlock adventures.</span>
